# Chemist SOP

  [bold]1.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] permitted to experiment with explosive mixtures;

  [bold]2.[/bold] Chemists in conjuction with [color=#5b97bc]Medical Doctors[/color] and must make sure that Cloning is stocked with Biomass if set up;

  [bold]3.[/bold] The Chemist must ensure that the Medbay is stocked with at least enough medication to handle Brute, Burn, Respiratory, and Toxin damage.

  [bold]4.[/bold] The Chemist is [bold]not[/bold] allowed to leave Chemistry unattended if the Medbay is devoid of Medication, except in such a case that Chemistry is unusable.
